// Title: Lateral Movement â€” Remote Service Creation
// Product: Sentinel | Defender for Endpoint
// ATT&CK: T1021 (Remote Services)
// Data Sources: DeviceProcessEvents
// Description: Detects potential lateral movement by identifying the creation of remote services or remote execution tools. Flags instances where sc.exe is used to create a service or psexec is executed, which may indicate lateral movement across devices.
// Author: Ahsan M.

DeviceProcessEvents
| where ProcessCommandLine has "sc.exe create"
    or ProcessCommandLine has "psexec"
| project Timestamp, DeviceName, AccountName, ProcessCommandLine
